'''Club Atlético San Cristóbal''',<ref name=LDF>{{cite web|url=http://ldf.com.do/air-europa-patrocinador-oficial-del-club-atletico-san-cristobal/|title=Air Europa, patrocinador oficial del Club Atlético San Cristóbal|trans-title=Air Europa, official sponsor of Club Atlético San Cristóbal|language=Spanish|publisher=[[Liga Dominicana de Fútbol]]|accessdate=27 April 2016}}</ref> commonly known as '''Atlético San Cristóbal''', are a Dominican Republic professional [[association football|football]] club which competes in the [[Liga Dominicana de Fútbol]]. It is currently also known as '''[[AirEuropa]] San Cristóbal''' for sponsorship reasons.<ref name=LDF/> They are based in The club is based in [[San Cristóbal, Dominican Republic|San Cristóbal]]. The club was established in 2015 after the [[Dominican Football Federation]] announced the creation of a professional league, the Liga Dominicana de Fútbol.

