The '''Canal Olímpic de Catalunya''' is a [[canal]] located in [[Castelldefels]], [[Catalonia]], [[Spain]]. Constructed in 1991, it hosted the [[Canoeing at the 1992 Summer Olympics|canoe sprint]] events for the [[1992 Summer Olympics]].
