{{infobox country at games | NPC = COL | NPCname = Colombian Paralympic Committee | games = Summer Paralympics | year = 1988 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.comiteparalimpicocolombiano.org }} | location = [[Seoul]] | competitors = 17 | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }} '''[[Colombia]]''' competed at the '''[[1988 Summer Paralympics]]''' in [[Seoul]], [[South Korea]]. 17 competitors from Colombia won no medals and so did not place in the [[1988 Summer Paralympics medal table|medal table]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.paralympic.org/colombia|title=Colombia - National Paralympic Committee|website=www.paralympic.org|access-date=2016-06-13}}</ref>
